---

<section id="services" style="position: relative; background: var(--c-bg-alt); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);">
  <div class="technical-grid gsap-stagger-container" style="border-top: 0; border-bottom: 0;">
    <div class="technical-item large-item gsap-fade-up" style="padding-top: 120px; padding-bottom: 60px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;">
      <div class="grid-overlay" style="opacity: 0.5;"></div>
      <div style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
        <div class="mono" style="color: var(--c-gold); margin-bottom: 24px;">/ 04 FIELD EXPERTISE</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--c-paper); letter-spacing: -0.02em; max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.1;">
          Core Services. <br><span style="color: var(--c-t3);">Survey execution.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/services" class="technical-item half-item gsap-stagger-item" style="opacity: 0;">
      <div style="font-family: var(--f-mono); color: var(--c-t3); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;">01 — ⌖</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-paper); margin-bottom: 16px;">Topographic Survey & Boundaries</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--c-t2); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">Measurement and verification of plot boundaries against legal deeds prior to transaction or development.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 40px; color: var(--c-gold); font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">
        [ Detail View ]
      </div>
    </a>
    
    <a href="/services" class="technical-item half-item gsap-stagger-item" style="opacity: 0;">
      <div style="font-family: var(--f-mono); color: var(--c-t3); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;">02 — ◬</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-paper); margin-bottom: 16px;">FMB Drawing Work</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--c-t2); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">Comparative analysis of site dimensions against government FMB records. Bank-compliant reporting.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 40px; color: var(--c-gold); font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">
        [ Detail View ]
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/services" class="technical-item half-item gsap-stagger-item" style="opacity: 0;">
      <div style="font-family: var(--f-mono); color: var(--c-t3); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;">03 — ⊕</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-paper); margin-bottom: 16px;">Construction Marking</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--c-t2); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">On-site column and wall demarcation directly from architectural drawings. Zero deviation tolerance.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 40px; color: var(--c-gold); font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">
        [ Detail View ]
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/services" class="technical-item half-item gsap-stagger-item" style="background: var(--c-bg); opacity: 0;">
      <div style="font-family: var(--f-mono); color: var(--c-gold); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;">+</div>
      <h3 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-paper); margin-bottom: 16px;">Full Service Index</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--c-t2); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">Topographical mapping, DGPS, Pipeline, and Highway surveying.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 40px; color: var(--c-gold); font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">
        [ View All 11 Services ]
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
